dataset.description: The City of Tacoma owns and operates two senior activity centers, Beacon Activity Center in the downtown area and Lighthouse Activity Center on the east side. Included data covers the type of fire, location, cause of the fire, call received and incident response times, information on the property type and use for structure and mobile fires, estimated property loss incurred.  Also included in the data set are details on the structure involved and specifics on the range of fire and smoke damage for structure fires, data on the type/model of vehicle for mobile fires or estimate on the size of the affected area for outside fires.
